5. MVP you could build now

Do not start with “all models.”
Start with one narrow but real stack.

Pantheon MVP v1

A multimodal coordinator with four subsystems:
	1.	LLM for reasoning and synthesis
	2.	VLM for image/screenshot understanding
	3.	Retriever for docs / memory / knowledge
	4.	Tool agent for actions

And Pantheon in the middle provides:
	•	routing
	•	translation schema
	•	memory
	•	constraint checks

MVP flow

User asks question
↓
Normalizer creates canonical request object
↓
Router chooses needed subsystems
↓
Each subsystem returns structured output
↓
Translator normalizes outputs
↓
Combinator merges them
↓
Constraint engine validates
↓
