8. What makes this different from a normal agent

A normal agent often does:
	•	decide tool
	•	call tool
	•	summarize result

Pantheon would do more:

Normal agent

single-threaded tool use

Pantheon nucleus
	•	multimodal translation
	•	multi-expert fusion
	•	structured memory
	•	explicit invariants
	•	cost-aware routing
	•	conflict resolution between models

So it is closer to:
agent framework + semantic bus + governance layer

