11. Best first use case

Do not try to solve “general intelligence.”

Build Pantheon first for a narrow high-value job, like:

Option A: Multimodal research copilot
	•	screenshot + doc + question
	•	returns grounded synthesis

Option B: Creative systems architect
	•	takes rough ideas
	•	routes through analogy, structure, critique, and implementation passes

Option C: Personal execution engine
	•	plans, routes to tools, tracks state, summarizes progress

For you, I’d start with A or B.

