12. Simplest real stack

A practical first stack would be:
	•	LLM: reasoning + synthesis
	•	Vision model: screenshot/image analysis
	•	Vector retrieval: memory/docs
	•	Workflow engine: route and call modules
	•	State store: JSON session/state log
	•	Rule engine: constraints and validation

That’s enough to prove the nucleus idea.

